<span class="code-folder">$ npx opencastle init</span>

<span class="code-comment"># Choose your IDE:</span>
<span class="code-folder">  1) VS Code      </span><span class="code-comment">— .github/ agents, instructions, skills</span>
<span class="code-folder">  2) Cursor       </span><span class="code-comment">— .cursorrules &amp; .cursor/rules/*.mdc</span>
<span class="code-folder">  3) Claude Code  </span><span class="code-comment">— CLAUDE.md &amp; .claude/ commands</span>

