<span class="code-folder">$ npx opencastle diff    </span><span class="code-comment"># Preview what update would change</span>
<span class="code-folder">$ npx opencastle eject   </span><span class="code-comment"># Remove dependency, keep files</span>
<span class="code-folder">$ npx opencastle run     </span><span class="code-comment"># Process task queue autonomously</span></pre>
